Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.00,0:00:21.32,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx80\3c&HFFFFFF&}掌上的微风 在光芒中一闪一闪地舞动
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.35,0:00:35.21,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx80\3c&HFFFFFF&}我已经能用全新的笑容 向陌生人道早安
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.24,0:00:47.43,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx80\3c&HFFFFFF&}尽管回忆溢满心头 我的朝气绝不认输
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.46,0:00:57.27,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx80\3c&HFFFFFF&}无所谓在干掉的泪痕中 有一扇通往梦想的门
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.30,0:01:01.28,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx80\3c&HFFFFFF&}如果烦恼就无法前进
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.31,0:01:10.03,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx80\3c&HFFFFFF&}没错 我会以迎接朋友的方式 温柔地微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.06,0:01:14.79,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx80\3c&HFFFFFF&}这是我们的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.82,0:01:23.88,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx80\3c&HFFFFFF&}无意间悲伤虽然涌上心头 我也会试着与人和好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.91,0:01:27.80,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx80\3c&HFFFFFF&}因为这是我们的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.78,0:01:27.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.55,0:01:40.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.19,0:01:43.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,响子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.86,0:01:50.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜你金榜题名
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.57,0:01:52.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个送给你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.01,0:01:58.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.88,0:02:04.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上了大学之后请穿穿看
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.55,0:02:06.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.00,0:02:21.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,响子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.71,0:02:33.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.34,0:03:13.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,#05响子焦虑不安!五代离家出走
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.35,0:03:19.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代还没回来吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.19,0:03:21.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经一个礼拜了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.39,0:03:25.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为现在是落榜通知的季节嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.93,0:03:28.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你们老是欺负他的关系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.60,0:03:30.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们才没有欺负他呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.63,0:03:35.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是实话实说罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.34,0:03:38.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这明明就是在欺负他嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.31,0:03:41.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过真叫人担心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.14,0:03:44.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟在这种时期…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.78,0:03:48.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等他全都落榜以后 就会回来了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.75,0:03:52.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代,你这样好吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.19,0:03:54.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.16,0:03:57.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你总不能这样一直逃避吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.36,0:04:01.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要是没考上一所大学 我就回不了一刻馆
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.50,0:04:05.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说你打算在我那里 赖到明年吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.40,0:04:09.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你刚才说什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.40,0:04:11.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂,你看那个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.21,0:04:14.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中了!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.71,0:04:17.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天晚上来开烧肉派对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.55,0:04:20.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁跟你吃烧肉啊 内裤比较重要,内裤
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.48,0:04:22.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内裤?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.45,0:04:26.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来开烧肉派对啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.89,0:04:29.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行,我要买新的内裤来穿
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.86,0:04:33.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我问你 你现在寄住在谁的家里啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.00,0:04:34.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.17,0:04:42.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借我一条内裤
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.37,0:04:44.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种东西怎么可以借人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.44,0:04:50.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些东西是我赢来的耶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.21,0:04:54.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猪头,要内裤回家拿不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.42,0:05:35.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钥匙…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.76,0:05:42.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没带
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.82,0:06:08.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.95,0:06:36.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好像玩得很开心嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.85,0:06:38.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是新的游戏吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.99,0:06:42.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦,内…内裤…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.23,0:06:46.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.00,0:06:50.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四…四谷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.94,0:06:58.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重考生莫名坠楼死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.77,0:07:00.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疑似受不了联考之苦而自杀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.58,0:07:08.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了,好像不是五代
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.72,0:07:09.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过他也太过份了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.98,0:07:13.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要外宿的话 至少也打通电话来不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.95,0:07:41.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惣一郎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.05,0:07:46.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惣一郎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.59,0:07:53.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惣一郎,这个怎么来的?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.38,0:08:15.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(投币式自助洗衣店)
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.02,0:08:23.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…好冷喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.16,0:08:32.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来我要用
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.83,0:09:01.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.93,0:09:03.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没穿内裤对不对?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.95,0:09:24.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个老太婆真夸张 这已经是第五盒了耶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.78,0:09:59.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂,五代?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.49,0:10:02.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代,你是五代吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.73,0:10:11.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在搞什么啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.70,0:10:15.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家担心到连饭都吃不下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.21,0:10:23.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之快点回来吧 大家都在等你喔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.25,0:10:28.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问,你是五代吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.25,0:10:33.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.98,0:11:00.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你是?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.11,0:11:00.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.54,0:11:34.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是一刻馆的?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.94,0:11:36.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是五代的?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.25,0:11:42.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢招待,吃饱了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.32,0:11:46.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的孙子平时承蒙你照顾了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.69,0:11:47.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里,别这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.39,0:11:49.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才常常受到五代的照顾呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.39,0:11:51.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…是我孙子受你照顾
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.06,0:11:53.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…是我受五代的照顾
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.80,0:11:55.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么这么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.40,0:11:57.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你实在太客气了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.00,0:12:01.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂,老太婆,碗公
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.44,0:12:02.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.84,0:12:09.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 让你提这么重的行李
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.74,0:12:10.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别客气
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.58,0:12:13.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为裕作会来接我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.45,0:12:14.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕作?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.68,0:12:16.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我孙子的名字啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.52,0:12:18.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重考生的?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.09,0:12:19.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不知道吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.52,0:12:22.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了,我想起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.53,0:12:26.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来他的名字不叫重考生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.09,0:12:27.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是当然的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.10,0:12:29.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个小鬼也真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.03,0:12:32.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两三天前信就应该已经寄到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.87,0:12:35.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他居然没有来接我 搞什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.97,0:12:40.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两三天前 他怎么可能看得到明信片
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.26,0:12:57.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阪本
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.23,0:12:58.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.16,0:12:59.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再让我住几天
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.06,0:13:02.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是无所谓啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.26,0:13:04.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过你这样好吗? 什么事?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.70,0:13:07.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少要跟管理员连络一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.90,0:13:10.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要跟我提到她!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.44,0:13:16.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经习惯 被朱美跟四谷他们嘲笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.25,0:13:21.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…可是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.08,0:13:23.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到管理员同情怜悯的眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.32,0:13:27.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很难受
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.42,0:13:29.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这实在太惨了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.29,0:13:32.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯,很惨
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.83,0:13:35.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是惨兮兮
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.70,0:13:39.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惨到谷底了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.24,0:13:44.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要重复说啦 这样会觉得越来越惨的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.02,0:13:58.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管理员
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.46,0:14:03.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走…走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.66,0:14:08.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代找到了没?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.13,0:14:13.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.10,0:14:15.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位是五代的奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.37,0:14:18.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你用不着这么大声 我听得到啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.24,0:14:23.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也进来喝杯咖啡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.14,0:14:24.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦?可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.95,0:14:27.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我请客
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.65,0:14:31.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱美,过来一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.36,0:14:37.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我马上就去,请你先进去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.33,0:14:43.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那真的是五代的奶奶?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.70,0:14:44.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.93,0:14:47.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以请暂时不要在她面前 提起五代的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.47,0:14:52.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道她迟早会知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.54,0:14:56.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我不想让 刚到这里没多久的奶奶担心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.18,0:14:57.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就会穿帮的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.71,0:15:01.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过,只要天黑之前 把他找回来就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.32,0:15:04.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想说的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.55,0:15:08.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请节哀顺变
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.83,0:15:14.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕作全部都落榜了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.70,0:15:16.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这只是时间的问题…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.20,0:15:21.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以,这一个礼拜…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.67,0:15:22.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四谷!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.94,0:15:25.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好啊,管理员
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.31,0:15:29.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么意思?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.68,0:15:32.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是多此一举
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.72,0:15:37.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.02,0:15:40.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊,把她弄哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.17,0:15:54.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.64,0:15:56.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.14,0:15:59.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他逃走了对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.11,0:16:01.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙会做什么事 我大概心里有数
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.95,0:16:07.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙没什么毅力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.62,0:16:09.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用担心啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.58,0:16:12.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他只是装得很烦恼的样子而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.32,0:16:14.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管理员,真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.72,0:16:18.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶都这么说了,错不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.03,0:16:20.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我又没有…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.76,0:16:22.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.20,0:16:24.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一刻馆的房客太冷漠了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.27,0:16:29.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,担心五代的 只有管理员一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.87,0:16:30.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老板!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.04,0:16:33.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么关系,他说的是实话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.64,0:16:36.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你们话中带刺
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.28,0:16:42.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶,你打算怎么办?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.08,0:16:44.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代不在这里的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.79,0:16:47.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么时候放榜?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.26,0:16:51.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天是最后一所私立大学放榜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.73,0:16:54.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,国立大学早就放榜了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.96,0:16:57.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,国立的根本考不上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.53,0:17:00.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天的放榜是关键
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.80,0:17:01.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想也是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.47,0:17:05.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果明天也落榜的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.64,0:17:11.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就把裕作带回去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.45,0:17:13.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是当然的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.98,0:17:18.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不是那种有钱人家 可以养光吃白饭的重考生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.62,0:17:25.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以后没有消遣对象了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.81,0:17:49.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思,还让你陪我来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.95,0:17:53.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这么说,希望他能考上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.49,0:17:58.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不想看到孙子哭丧的脸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.60,0:18:14.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了… 好棒喔…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.15,0:18:28.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样?奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.33,0:18:33.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶,到底怎么样?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.60,0:18:44.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.67,0:18:49.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管理员,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.28,0:18:50.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.28,0:18:53.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.35,0:18:54.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.02,0:18:57.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕作的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.32,0:18:59.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.22,0:19:00.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道他的准考证号码
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.77,0:19:13.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇,人山人海
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.27,0:19:15.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样什么都看不到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.54,0:19:17.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等人潮退了再来看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.61,0:19:20.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋,我没有那么悠哉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.91,0:19:28.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶,有没有看到?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.05,0:19:33.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起喔 裕作应该会来看榜才对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.15,0:19:34.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.36,0:19:36.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上去罗,五代 好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.83,0:19:40.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好,阪本,就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.93,0:19:42.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少废话,快点看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.41,0:19:53.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂,五代,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.67,0:19:54.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕作!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.58,0:19:55.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追啊,快追!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.01,0:19:56.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.18,0:20:00.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.22,0:20:08.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕作
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.82,0:20:11.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.79,0:20:15.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.03,0:20:18.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个笨蛋!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.87,0:20:22.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶和管理员
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.47,0:20:26.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是,为什么奶奶会在这里?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.61,0:20:28.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个都无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.58,0:20:30.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底有没有考上?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.48,0:20:33.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说啊说啊,到底有没有考上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.45,0:20:35.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还没看啦!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.05,0:20:40.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个没出息的家伙 到底在搞什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.39,0:20:42.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要打我啦 头壳会被你打坏的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.06,0:20:43.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少废话!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.62,0:20:44.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.33,0:20:47.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人潮好像少了点
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.46,0:20:48.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.86,0:20:50.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧,五代
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.00,0:21:26.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考上了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.87,0:21:31.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考上了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.92,0:21:43.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管理员…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.33,0:21:56.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈,不要跳了啦,太丢脸了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.06,0:21:59.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶,不要跳了啦,太丢脸了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.44,0:22:03.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全跟不上他们的步调
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.84,0:22:06.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚大概会被他们牵着走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.17,0:22:07.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想也是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.41,0:22:12.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这样也很好啊 有人让我们继续消遣下去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.88,0:22:17.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为五代是我的玩具
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.32,0:22:21.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来,大家请尽量喝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.32,0:22:22.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天特别宽待
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.72,0:22:24.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管理员
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.09,0:22:25.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.70,0:22:33.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要干什么? 放开我!放开我!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.44,0:22:36.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.04,0:22:37.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.38,0:22:44.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.45,0:22:46.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代,这个给你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.65,0:22:50.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经洗干净了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.82,0:22:53.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管理员
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.39,0:22:58.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么东西?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.16,0:23:00.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊对啊,什么东西?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.73,0:23:02.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.86,0:23:04.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕作,你又干了什么好事吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.90,0:23:06.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶,你误会了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.03,0:23:08.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的没有什么
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.67,0:23:10.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么到底是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.34,0:23:13.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的不是你们想像的那种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.01,0:23:16.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们想像的是什么东西?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.51,0:23:18.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦?这个嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.28,0:23:20.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝吧,管理员,喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.98,0:23:23.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就尽情地喝吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.58,0:23:26.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好耶,喝个痛快,喝个痛快
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.99,0:23:28.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.86,0:23:30.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管理员…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.30,0:23:30.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.96,0:23:54.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代考上了大学 一刻馆的春天也终于到了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.20,0:23:58.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过樱花的季节 对我来说是很难受的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.63,0:24:02.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相聚一刻下一回 ‘春天的冲击!响子的秘密!’
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.67,0:24:04.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.11,0:24:06.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不,这个下个礼拜再说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.77,0:24:06.77,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.41,0:24:35.69,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx87}为何你能如此若无其事
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.72,0:24:43.03,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx87}光只是眨个眼 就能让我悸动不已
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.06,0:24:51.62,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx87}使我身陷险境
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.28,0:25:06.30,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx87}明明已经可以相爱 偏偏时机还不成熟
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.33,0:25:18.56,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx87}我快要忍受不了 快要变成了愚蠢的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.60,0:25:23.94,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx87}真是痛苦的折磨

